{"tid":1487504,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恆指8，9月認真討論","createTime":"2019-08-19T09:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T13:24:06.000Z","uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9289c984606013c42392c1d2830ffc8617da452","tid":1487504,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"由7月開始跌，去到約25200左右<br />\n一直起呢個位浮沉好幾日<br />\n<br />\n呢段期間再次出現環球債市，美債市倒掛<br />\n恐慌指數同埋金價一路上揚，<br />\n但係感覺恆指完全反映唔到外圍局勢<br />\n<br />\n淨係睇隻388，由6，7月開始成交額一路下跌<br />\n雖然有跟過恆指大盤跌而由280左右去到23x左右價位<br />\n<br />\n但呢幾日既反彈，足足升左20蚊差唔多10%<br />\n<br />\n淨流入既力度非常強勁<br />\n<br />\n想同大家討論下究竟係壓彈弓既力所以有咁樣既技術反彈<br />\n定係有國家隊因素，好可能會繼續破頂去到見27000<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a69231f5692bcaef9e8d13a23768da421e99758","tid":1487504,"uid":91813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"大戶望撚住牛熊圖黎玩"},{"pid":"0914e025ca8e6795697075a4ebf775809b08bf81","tid":1487504,"uid":89225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"恒指十年如一日都仲有人玩<br />\n等於響個屎塔搵下堆屎睇下會唔會有金執一樣"},{"pid":"f0e66240fe261c7c26d7a98144d322a0e93c032c","tid":1487504,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"成份股一做反彈浪大戶會做野 好難用外圍黎睇佢短期點走"},{"pid":"a791f81abb543617edacfe0bf0bcb15c7fee1448","tid":1487504,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">823</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fESbQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fESbQo.jpg&h=c5df1785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">824</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKWk5aO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKWk5aO.jpg&h=16b